replies.msg:
Ronaldo to Financial Times on a tactical advise he got from Silvio Berlusconi when he was at Milan: &quot;Why did you never make a goal from the corner? It&rsquo;s so easy. Put everybody outside the area and when he kicks it, everybody go into the  penalty box!&quot;<br />
<br />
Ronaldo: &quot;When Silvio said something, everybody said, &lsquo;OK, we will do it.&rsquo; But after that we came back to our way.&quot;

